
{{alias}}( x )
    Reverses the order of elements along the second-to-last dimension of a four-
    dimensional nested input array.

    The function does *not* perform a deep copy of nested array elements.

    Parameters
    ----------
    x: ArrayLikeObject
        Input nested array.

    Returns
    -------
    out: Array
        Output array.

    Examples
    --------
    > var out = {{alias}}( [ [ [ [ 1, 2 ], [ 3, 4 ] ] ] ] )
    [ [ [ [ 3, 4 ], [ 1, 2 ] ] ] ]
